    'rag_pipeline': 'Basic RAG',
    'reference': 'Interna medicina (6. izd., str. XXXVIII, 1693). (2022). Medicinska fakulteta; Buča.',
    'question': '6. The sensation of difficult breathing reported by the patient in the medical history is best described by the term: a. Orthopnea b. Tachypnea c. Dyspnea d. Platypnea e. Trepopnea',
    'text_answer': 'Dyspnea',
    'topic_text': '6. The sensation of difficult breathing reported by the patient in the medical history is best described by the term: a. Orthopnea b. Tachypnea c. Dyspnea d. Platypnea e. Trepopnea',
    'context': 'Opredelitev. Dispneja je občutek neuspešnega in neprijetnega povečanega napora pri dihanju. Etiologija. Je pogost simptom pri boleznih dihal ter bolezni srca. Dispneja je tudi simptom slabokrvnosti ali bolezni dihalnih mišic. Pogosta je tudi psihogena dispneja. English: Definition. Dyspnea is the sensation of an unsuccessful and unpleasantly increased effort during breathing. Etiology. It is a common symptom in respiratory diseases and heart diseases. Dyspnea is also a symptom of anemia or of diseases of the respiratory muscles. Psychogenic dyspnea is also frequent.',
    'text': 'Context: Opredelitev. Dispneja je občutek neuspešnega in neprijetnega povečanega napora pri dihanju. Etiologija. Je pogost simptom pri boleznih dihal ter bolezni srca. Dispneja je tudi simptom slabokrvnosti ali bolezni dihalnih mišic. Pogosta je tudi psihogena dispneja. English: Definition. Dyspnea is the sensation of an unsuccessful and unpleasantly increased effort during breathing. Etiology. It is a common symptom in respiratory diseases and heart diseases. Dyspnea is also a symptom of anemia or of diseases of the respiratory muscles. Psychogenic dyspnea is also frequent. Supporting answer: Dyspnea'
  },
{
    'id': 7,
    'source_dataset': 'ChatMED-Project/RAGCare-QA',
    'tenant_id': 'hospital-heart',
    'specialty': 'Cardiology',
    'complexity': 'basic',
    'case_priority': 'high',
    'case_status': 'review',
    'rag_pipeline': 'Basic RAG',
    'reference': 'Interna medicina (6. izd., str. XXXVIII, 1693). (2022). Medicinska fakulteta; Buča.',
    'question': '7. Which laboratory test can we use in clinical practice to confirm heart failure as the cause of exertional dyspnea? a. Troponin T b. Troponin I c. Atrial natriuretic peptide (ANP) d. Brain (B-type) natriuretic peptide (BNP) e. Erythropoietin',
    'text_answer': 'Brain (B-type) natriuretic peptide (BNP)',
    'topic_text': '7. Which laboratory test can we use in clinical practice to confirm heart failure as the cause of exertional dyspnea? a. Troponin T b. Troponin I c. Atrial natriuretic peptide (ANP) d. Brain (B-type) natriuretic peptide (BNP) e. Erythropoietin',
    'context': 'Neposredno lahko srčno popuščanje (tudi akutno) potrdimo le s povišanimi vrednostmi možganskega natriuretičnega peptida (BNP) ali NT-odlomka prekurzorja BNP (NT-proBNP), ki sta pri teh bolnikih značilno povišana (normalne vrednosti so odvisne od spola, starosti in laboratorijske metode). English: Heart failure (even acute) can be confirmed directly only by elevated levels of brain natriuretic peptide (BNP) or the N-terminal fragment of the BNP precursor (NT-proBNP), both of which are characteristically increased in these patients (normal values depend on sex, age, and the laboratory method).',
    'text': 'Context: Neposredno lahko srčno popuščanje (tudi akutno) potrdimo le s povišanimi vrednostmi možganskega natriuretičnega peptida (BNP) ali NT-odlomka prekurzorja BNP (NT-proBNP), ki sta pri teh bolnikih značilno povišana (normalne vrednosti so odvisne od spola, starosti in laboratorijske metode). English: Heart failure (even acute) can be confirmed directly only by elevated levels of brain natriuretic peptide (BNP) or the N-terminal fragment of the BNP precursor (NT-proBNP), both of which are characteristically increased in these patients (normal values depend on sex, age, and the laboratory method). Supporting answer: Brain (B-type) natriuretic peptide (BNP)'
  },
{
    'id': 8,
    'source_dataset': 'ChatMED-Project/RAGCare-QA',
    'tenant_id': 'hospital-heart',
    'specialty': 'Cardiology',
    'complexity': 'basic',
